data.description: Welcome Home to the charming Forest Lakes of Chelsea! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence sits on a spacious corner lot, offering a serene escape. The fenced backyard with a covered patio is perfect for outdoor gatherings. Step inside to discover custom cabinets, closets, crown molding, and gleaming hardwood floors that make you feel at home. The marble fireplace surround and soaring ceilings create an inviting ambiance with an abundance of natural light. The main floor boasts a master suite with a double vanity and a relaxing garden tub. Upstairs, two more bedrooms and an office/study provide comfort and privacy. Forest Lakes is a true gem, with walking trails, a playground, and a picturesque lake for fishing. And being on the North side of Chelsea takes valuable minutes off your daily commute. This is your chance to own a piece of Shelby County's finest. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make it yours!
